                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7874" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">HRM-0530</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2277 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">歌芮斯的别出心“裁”：裁掉的是成本还是人心？</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Grace&#39;s disguised downsizing: Is it the cost or support that is cut?</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">卫旭华，王敏，杜玉娇，李松，孙蓉，杨沫，林少鹏，潘莉莉，刘静</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">兰州大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">歌芮斯内衣（汕头）有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">纺织工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">人力资源部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">歌芮斯；裁员；员工关系管理；危机防范</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Grace；Downsizing；Employee Relationship Management；Crisis Prevention</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例以歌芮斯在产业调整过程中的员工关系管理实践为主线，讲述了歌芮斯因缩减成本“变相裁员”而陷入内部危机并采取行动摆脱危机的故事。首先，案例介绍了歌芮斯公司成为业界翘楚的发展历程。随后，以产业调整为背景，讲述了当歌芮斯面临新基地投产，而不得不缩减旧基地规模的困境时，如何利用花样百出的手段“变相裁员”，致使公司内部水深火热，以至于诱发了员工跳楼、集体罢工的重大事件。最后，歌芮斯力挽狂澜，重拾员工信心，却因新一轮产业调整，迎来了新的员工关系管理挑战。案例通过讲述歌芮斯在事前、事中、事后的员工关系变化，揭示了像歌芮斯这样的公司在经历产业调整后可能引发的员工关系问题，对产业调整期的企业员工关系管理实践具有一定启示作用。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case focused on the employee relations management practices of Grace during the industrial adjustment process. We narrated the story of Grace &#39; internal crisis due to cost-cutting and &quot;disguised downsizing,&quot; and the actions taken to overcome the crisis. First, the case introduced the history of the company&#39;s development into an industry leader. Then, in the context of industrial adjustment, we showed how Grace used a variety of tactics to &quot; disguised downsizing &quot; in order to cope with the dilemma of having to reduce the size of the old base due to the commissioning of the new base. As a result, the company was in deep distress, which induced a major incident of employees attempt to jump buildings and collective strikes. Finally, the company was able to regain the confidence of its employees, but a new round of industrial adjustment brought new challenges in employee relations management. The case revealed the employee relations problems that may arise in a company like Grace after industrial adjustment by describing the changes in employee relations at Grace before, during, and after the incident, and it is instructive for the practice of employee relations management in companies during industrial adjustment.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,博士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《人力资源管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">裁员与员工优化；员工关系管理；危机下的员工关系管理</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-12</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
